5 forks - This is a delicious recipe - I made it for 14 and then 32! Easy to multiply for a crowd. You can make ahead up to searing the meat and then put aside for roasting. I added mushrooms to veggies and you don't need to multiply the sauce as many times as the meat. Just wonderful recipe any time of year.

