4 forks plus - This is absolutely delicious! I made for 14 and then made again for 32! Its so easy - do ahead up to where you sear the meat then put aside for roasting. I added sliced mushrooms to veggies and when you multiply recipe you don't need to multiply the sauce. Just dump the large can of ground tomatoes in (with wine, etc). I served with noodles and is wonderful as left- overs. An all-year recipe to enjoy.

